description: This Chainlink VRF top 2% rating Gatinho purrs with a rating of 80, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 160, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, Leverage for East, 1 for South, and Leverage for West. Gatinho has the personality suit of punter. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gatinho [160 Votes, Top 2% Rating]
